Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.92,0:00:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掌上的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.73,0:00:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在光芒中一閃一閃地舞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.33,0:00:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.31,0:00:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.98,0:00:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管回憶溢滿心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.99,0:00:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的朝氣絕不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.73,0:00:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂在乾掉的淚痕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.00,0:00:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一扇通往夢想的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.04,0:01:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果煩惱就無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.24,0:01:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.61,0:01:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會以迎接朋友的方式\N溫柔地微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.05,0:01:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.79,0:01:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無意間悲傷雖然湧上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.22,0:01:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也會試著與人和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.70,0:01:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.74,0:02:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰來表演個餘興節目好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.47,0:02:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺氣氛實在很冷清
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.11,0:02:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你沒有什麼有趣的事可說嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.65,0:02:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如說管理員討厭你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.78,0:02:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是家教被炒魷魚了之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.25,0:02:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這哪裡有趣了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.85,0:02:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你們幾個\N幹嘛老是在別人的房間鬼混?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.79,0:02:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是受不了\N這實在太不健康了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.23,0:02:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星期日大白天的就這付德行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.03,0:02:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照這樣下去,我一定會完蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.27,0:02:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.77,0:02:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來他認為自己還沒完蛋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.61,0:02:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼說都隨你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.01,0:02:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有什麼有趣的事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.75,0:02:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.12,0:02:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在嗎?我是貨運公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.49,0:02:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貨運公司?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.96,0:02:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.99,0:03:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等你們來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.96,0:03:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要放在哪裡呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.13,0:03:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放在裡面,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.54,0:03:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#37 危險的變裝大會!\N響子也激烈大變身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.21,0:03:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了\N辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.33,0:03:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.53,0:03:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…請放心\N他們是這裡的房客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.40,0:03:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們這是幹嘛?\N怎麼穿著睡衣就出來呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.77,0:03:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好大驚小怪的\N我們一直都是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.17,0:03:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛故意裝模作樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.01,0:03:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是有外面的人在耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.24,0:03:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很高興吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.38,0:03:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…哦,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.61,0:03:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼,真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.35,0:03:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.85,0:03:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有資格說別人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.75,0:04:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年紀輕輕的就過這種生活\N以後會完蛋的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.19,0:04:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也在擔心這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.69,0:04:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你早就已經完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.69,0:04:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.56,0:04:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,妳買了什麼東西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.63,0:04:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鏡台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.70,0:04:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事不值得大家聚集在這裡\N請上二樓去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.34,0:04:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鏡台被賣掉真叫人傷心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.77,0:04:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想念安壽,好想念廚子王啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.94,0:04:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是鏡台,應該是''兄弟''吧\N(''鏡台''音近''兄弟'')
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.24,0:04:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,跟他說也沒用的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.48,0:04:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝,真的辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.98,0:04:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,哪裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.46,0:04:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,真的好丟臉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.06,0:04:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.93,0:04:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去打棒球嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.00,0:04:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要跟時計坡第二小學\N打決賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.47,0:04:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好,賢太郎很健康
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.27,0:04:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟其他的房客不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.82,0:05:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員能待在這裡\N我真的很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.82,0:05:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裡的正常人\N只有我跟管理員而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.63,0:05:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答應我,妳會一直待在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.36,0:05:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.43,0:05:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.20,0:05:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.64,0:05:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比賽加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.97,0:05:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,我們說好了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.76,0:05:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.20,0:05:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直希望有個\N能照到全身的鏡子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.58,0:06:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.08,0:06:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高中制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.95,0:06:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來我有帶來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.92,0:06:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.49,0:06:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.96,0:07:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上課的時候\N我有些地方不太懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.53,0:07:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好像很常來問我問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.14,0:07:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,我很喜歡地質學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.31,0:07:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實,我根本不在乎上課的內容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.29,0:08:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,這樣就完美無瑕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.49,0:08:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,一起來喝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.90,0:08:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,快來啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.54,0:08:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.75,0:08:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.88,0:08:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我只是穿穿看而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.12,0:08:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來妳有這種興趣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.52,0:08:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是興趣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.42,0:08:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你們出去一下\N我要換衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.10,0:08:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧,穿這個模樣來喝酒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.27,0:08:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼\N我才不會在大白天就喝酒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.77,0:08:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳就別裝了,沒有喝醉酒\N妳都敢穿這種衣服還說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.25,0:08:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,妳好可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.45,0:08:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭,不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.22,0:09:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可愛?好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.69,0:09:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要去哪裡?\N馬上就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.89,0:09:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧,管理員\N我們來飲酒作樂吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.52,0:09:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.76,0:09:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別害怕,別害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.12,0:09:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代也很喜歡妳這付打扮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.59,0:09:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.83,0:09:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.46,0:09:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你們,讓我換個衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.23,0:09:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一有人來了怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會有人來的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.47,0:09:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來這個假日\N會變得意外地有趣喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.91,0:09:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.05,0:09:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.95,0:09:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道該怎麼說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.79,0:09:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老實說,我酒都醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.66,0:09:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好高興喔,還很合身耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.73,0:09:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來妳以前就是這種體型啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.20,0:09:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能輸給妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.23,0:09:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的高中制服也還在嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.14,0:09:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我們來玩別的遊戲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.47,0:09:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有比這個遊戲更好玩的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.11,0:09:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.88,0:10:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係呢,就先這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.88,0:10:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走,喝酒喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.78,0:10:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.38,0:10:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人偶爾要盡情地嬉鬧一番才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.73,0:10:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這身袈裟哪裡來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.40,0:10:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祕密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.07,0:10:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,你穿袈裟還蠻適合的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.74,0:10:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.94,0:10:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一群大人\N居然大白天就在玩這種遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.24,0:10:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係,反正是禮拜天嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.65,0:10:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都有病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.25,0:10:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說嘛,居然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.48,0:10:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做這種蠢事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.82,0:10:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋不死是好不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.72,0:10:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來來,管理員,坐這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.53,0:10:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,啤酒啤酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.76,0:10:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是是,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.80,0:10:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我朋友在酒店工作的制服\N我跟她要來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.10,0:10:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣?好不好看?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.67,0:11:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,愛染桂\N(描述護士與醫生戀情的電影名稱)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.37,0:11:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.28,0:11:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得秩序被搗亂了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.44,0:11:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯,這裡有個叛徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.68,0:11:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.78,0:11:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你一個人想裝正經\N這可不行喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.82,0:11:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連管理員雖然一邊說著\N''不要不要''
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.19,0:11:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是也乖乖地加入了\N你不覺得她很可憐嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.73,0:11:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得我可憐的話\N就讓我去換衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.23,0:11:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有學生服吧,快去換
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.30,0:11:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,妳看過我的衣櫃了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.04,0:11:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你還留著學生服呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.84,0:11:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我奶奶寄來的\N叫我穿去參加補習班的入學典禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.38,0:11:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶還真是用心良苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.95,0:11:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,快去換\N跟我組成一對高中男女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.08,0:11:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.62,0:11:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.82,0:11:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.59,0:11:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,怎麼連你都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.39,0:11:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要阻止我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.73,0:12:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可以讓妳一個人難堪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.53,0:12:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶,說得好,棒極了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.16,0:12:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐,妳怎麼這麼安靜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.10,0:12:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼心事\N儘管跟護士姊姊說喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.10,0:12:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,等你很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.20,0:12:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這實在太驚人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.74,0:12:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同學,到這裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.81,0:12:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.21,0:12:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶,開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.14,0:12:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贏了好高興,鮮花一朵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.02,0:12:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是一對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.35,0:12:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.52,0:12:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.52,0:13:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來商量吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.00,0:13:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨…惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.88,0:13:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竹籠竹籠…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.39,0:13:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,護士小姐,快幫我看看\N我的臉變成這樣了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.76,0:13:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,立刻動手術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.19,0:13:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到竟然鬧成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.96,0:13:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.63,0:13:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在家嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.47,0:13:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像有人來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.37,0:13:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在家嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.67,0:13:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是三鷹教練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.74,0:13:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,快去給他開門吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.21,0:13:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我很困擾…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.98,0:13:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳跟他有約嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.75,0:13:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.55,0:13:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去叫他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.45,0:13:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,我去給他開門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.72,0:14:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢著!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.62,0:14:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳想要怎麼做?\N要不要叫他回去?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.45,0:14:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.56,0:14:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?不在?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.76,0:14:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的不在嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.56,0:14:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你不相信我說的話?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.90,0:14:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.40,0:14:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.50,0:14:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本還想幫你傳話給她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.47,0:14:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算有,我也不會跟你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.21,0:14:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,螃蟹螃蟹,有什麼事嗎?螃蟹\N(''螃蟹螃蟹''音近''二樓'')
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.28,0:14:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我傳話嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.51,0:14:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是路過順便來看看她而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.89,0:14:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.99,0:14:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實,我也不太知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.76,0:14:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你還穿這種衣服嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.43,0:14:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年輕醫生,原來你在這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.10,0:14:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,快來,病患不得了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.77,0:14:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?年輕醫生?等等…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.57,0:14:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.54,0:14:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位太太,不要這麼慌亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.77,0:14:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾,已經沒救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.91,0:14:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…我不相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.04,0:15:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親戚們都在等\N來,我們一起走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.35,0:15:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,往這裡走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.52,0:15:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浩三大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.25,0:15:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浩三大人是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.29,0:15:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.73,0:15:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.77,0:15:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,浩三大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.81,0:15:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太太,斬斷這份情絲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.11,0:15:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情絲是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.42,0:15:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,門簾的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.92,0:15:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢業後也要繼續寫交換日記喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.92,0:15:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.82,0:15:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,你們兩個高中生情侶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.16,0:15:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以喝酒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.53,0:15:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳才是呢\N女學生還拿著一大瓶酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.76,0:15:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?我是訓導處的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.50,0:16:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然是訓導處的\N就要有訓導處的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.77,0:16:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是說了\N我是訓導處的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.64,0:16:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.68,0:16:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.64,0:16:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.68,0:16:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種訓導處的人\N最好別跟她扯上關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.01,0:16:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.02,0:16:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.25,0:16:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我警告過你了,很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.89,0:16:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,有個高中生昏倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.99,0:16:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,讓開讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.19,0:16:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.96,0:16:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,他是因為失戀打擊太大猝死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.63,0:16:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這實在令人傷心\N就讓貧僧來念佛送他上西天吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.47,0:16:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要這麼暴力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.14,0:16:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛,管理員\N這是青春偶像劇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.74,0:16:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.25,0:16:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.01,0:16:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是電話響了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.52,0:16:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以接電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.35,0:16:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯,不要接
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.92,0:16:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是不良少年要找妳出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.82,0:16:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能在這裡認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.56,0:16:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要重新振作,音無
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.42,0:16:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.06,0:16:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看,那就是\N不良少年的悲慘下場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.70,0:17:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,萬一是緊急聯絡\N那就不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.40,0:17:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,我還是接一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.33,0:17:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.30,0:17:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一巴掌,兩巴掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.74,0:17:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼打她巴掌呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.71,0:17:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,爸爸都這麼說了\N妳還是聽不懂嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.81,0:17:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看著爸爸的眼睛回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.96,0:17:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是\N音無小姐出了什麼事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.70,0:17:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這所學校是由我掌控的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.34,0:17:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,終於露出真面目了\N你這個旁觀棋客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.91,0:17:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.65,0:17:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.62,0:17:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險,危險\N因為太危險了,請退下喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.79,0:18:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險,太危險了\N快點退下,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.09,0:18:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡,那是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.63,0:18:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要使喚我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.66,0:18:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的水蜜桃罐頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.27,0:18:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分一點給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.70,0:18:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冬天到了\N光輝奪目的水蜜桃罐頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.67,0:18:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蔚藍的青空,雪白的水蜜桃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.45,0:18:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青花魚罐頭就算了\N唯有這個水蜜桃罐頭不能讓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.45,0:18:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生離死別的大哥\N我好想你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.07,0:18:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音…音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.21,0:18:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,傳球,傳球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.01,0:18:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年輕醫生,儘管喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.05,0:19:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.25,0:19:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次又在鬧什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.02,0:19:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.76,0:19:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷,你這是幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.16,0:19:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想把水蜜桃罐頭送給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.93,0:19:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要送給我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.93,0:19:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是把罐頭抬起來而已\N(''抬起來''音同''送給你'')
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.90,0:19:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.14,0:19:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳球傳球…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.28,0:19:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前我就想跟妳說一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.58,0:19:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我一定要說清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.08,0:19:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.25,0:19:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定有比這裡\N更適合妳的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.92,0:19:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛情青春偶像劇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.36,0:19:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定能為妳準備\N更適合妳的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.90,0:19:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯,妳一定能變成\N世界級的選手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.20,0:19:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯,阿丘,擊出愛司球吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.44,0:19:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油,喔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.40,0:19:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是!\N我是很認真的在跟響子講話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.04,0:20:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千萬不要被他騙了\N走,我們一起逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.31,0:20:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡,不准逃\N站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.25,0:20:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,護士長,把這位病患\N帶去隔壁病棟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.12,0:20:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要立刻為他動手術\N先幫他打麻醉針,聽到沒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.99,0:20:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是,醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.12,0:20:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.46,0:20:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我,我最討厭大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.43,0:20:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.66,0:20:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醫生,請讓我也去隔壁病棟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.34,0:20:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題,我允許妳外出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.94,0:20:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們去看得見港灣的高台\N一起用餐如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.87,0:20:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡\N我要以濫用職權的罪名逮捕你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.71,0:20:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啤酒兩打,清酒五瓶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.18,0:20:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好,我是經不起賄賂的訓導處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.85,0:20:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.12,0:20:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,真是花了好大的功夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.02,0:20:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.16,0:20:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.42,0:20:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.79,0:20:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.59,0:20:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.69,0:20:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝著夕陽?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.23,0:20:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧,這裡又不是海邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.38,0:21:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞬，去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.48,0:21:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…好清爽的風啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.82,0:21:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,白雲啊,你要去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.63,0:21:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了\N媽媽,我肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.30,0:21:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.57,0:21:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還在喝酒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.74,0:21:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶好耶,打啊打啊…\N加油加油…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.68,0:21:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然用這種卑鄙的手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.05,0:21:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才是呢\N居然想用金錢收買她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.86,0:21:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你們兩個,不要再打了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.22,0:21:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們打啦\N這是友情的表現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.54,0:22:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還蠻能打的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.80,0:22:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也不弱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.01,0:22:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.01,0:22:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都別說了\N這才叫青春啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.48,0:22:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.05,0:22:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,各位,看那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.96,0:22:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝著那道夕陽盡情奔跑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.36,0:22:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶,青春,我們要享受青春…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.04,0:22:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賢太郎,你在發什麼呆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.01,0:22:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看,媽媽很年輕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.25,0:22:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賢…賢太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.18,0:22:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我原本以為\N至少管理員是正常的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.05,0:22:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你誤會了,這是有原因的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.62,0:23:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是管理員先開始的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.43,0:23:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賢太郎,等一下!!\N聽我解釋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.20,0:23:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賢太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.26,0:23:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係,這就是青春啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.87,0:23:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賢太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.44,0:23:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個星期天真是棒透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.24,0:23:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是醫院羅曼史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.01,0:23:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要,請不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.12,0:23:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡,總有一天\N我要離開這種公寓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.97,0:23:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是以朋友的感覺相處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.61,0:23:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當說出''我喜歡妳''之後\N一切都結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.58,0:23:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛就好像賭博一樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.88,0:24:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.58,0:24:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「五代失戀?\N小津江突然接近三鷹?」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.12,0:24:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,男生和女生\N道別時的表現是很重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.97,0:24:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當我們互相凝視時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.64,0:24:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會有一道奇妙的旋律\N在心中迴響著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.38,0:24:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法用言語來表達愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.06,0:24:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只好彈奏起了鋼琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.66,0:24:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請把夢丟進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.03,0:24:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為我測量一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.77,0:24:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛有多深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:58.64,0:25:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用輕觸的嘴唇演奏著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.81,0:25:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平靜的合聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.02,0:25:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使擁抱著妳依然惆悵滿懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:17.93,0:25:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢見了Fantasy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:24.93,0:25:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開啟了只有我們兩人\N才看得見的門扉Fantasy
